”What is pin A5.”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: uno pin guide
des: Let Alexa help you find the correct pin on your UNO. Especially helpful when you are pinching three finicky wires together on the breadboard and your is lap full of loose components. Make sure that pin is the one you want before you solder it. The skill also has basic explanations of PWM, the serial bus, SPI and I2C as well as digital and analog.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
